name: Victorian Romantic Yellow Ribbon Rose With Mother Of Pearl And Yellow And Green Crystal Earrings
description:
These beautiful and romantic earrings are made with 6mm cream glass pearls, 4mm peridot satin Swarovski crystals and bright yellow ribbon roses attached to 20mm mother of pearls discs. 8mm cream glass pearls and 4 mm peridot satin Swarovski bicone crystals hang beneath.

The earrings measure 2 3/8  inches in length and are on silver over brass leverback earwires.

name: Victorian Peach Ribbon Flower Designer Necklace Cream Glass Pearls Peach And Light Brown Crystals
description:
A beautiful peach flower made of ribbon nestles in the center of a beadwoven pendant that is comprised of 6mm cream glass pearls, 4mm and 3mm rose peach Swarovski crystals, 3mm light smoked topaz Swarovski crystals, light gold seed beads and gold plated tube beads. 6mm and 8mm cream glass pearls, 4mm peach rose and light smoked topaz crystals, hang from the bottom of the pendant on gold plated components.

The focal flower component is 1 1/2 inches in diameter and the whole pendant measures 4 1/4 inches in length.

name: Orange Ribbon Roses And Crystals Gold Designer Glass Pearl Necklace
description:
This adorable necklace is created with sweet orange ribbon roses of varying shades on gold plated metal components, 17x8mm, 10mm, 8mm orange glass pearls and 4mm peridot satin Swarovski crystals.

This double strand necklace measure 16 inches in length.

This bold necklace is sure to get comments.

name: Orange Ribbon Roses And Crystals Gold Handmade Designer Glass Pearl Earrings

They measure approximately 3 1/4 inches in length and are on gold plated brass leverback earwires.

These bold earring are sure to get comments.

This bracelet measures 6 1/2  inches in length and has a 1 1/2 inch extender.

name: Light Blue Swarovski Crystal Pearl And Crystal Rondelle Fashion Necklace

The earrings measure just a touch under 3 1/2 inches long. The woven component is almost 1 inch wide and the earwires are gold over brass.

The necklace measures just a touch under 16 inches long. The woven and drop measures 3 1/2 inches long.

The beaded beads are sewn together and are comprised of 4mm light sapphire satin Swarovski crystal bicones, 4mm blue glass pearls, 12mm gunmetal bugle beads, 4mm daisy spacers and seed beads. The bracelet is strung with 12mm pewter colored glass pearls, vitrail Czech glass rondelles and silver plated embellishments on stretch cord. 

This bracelet measures 7 inches.

This bracelet is a design that Laura had featured in Bead And Button Magazine.
